        <num>2770</num>
        <heading>Agreements relating to payment in lieu of taxes</heading>
        <subsection eId="sec_2770__subsec_i">
          <num>(i)</num>
          <content>
            <p>the amount of such annual payments\nin lieu of taxes, (ii) whether the use of such property is for purposes\nother than public aviation purposes and (iii) the extent to which such\nproperty is used for purposes other than public aviation purposes. In\nmaking such determinations the authority shall take into consideration\nthe recommendations, if any, of the county.\n</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
